ALUTECH  1.0

984 typedef struct DMA_MemMap {
985  uint8_t RESERVED_0[256];
986  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
987  uint32_t SAR;
988  uint32_t DAR;
989  union { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
990  uint32_t DSR_BCR;
991  struct { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
992  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
993  uint8_t DSR;
994  } DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT;
995  };
996  uint32_t DCR;
997  } DMA[4];
998 } volatile *DMA_MemMapPtr;

1261  uint32_t PCSR;
1262  struct { /* offset: 0x20, array step: 0x10 */
1263  uint32_t COMP;
1264  uint32_t MASK;
1265  uint32_t FUNCTION;
1266  uint8_t RESERVED_0[4];
1267  } COMPARATOR[2];
1268 } volatile *DWT_MemMapPtr;
1269

1272  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- */

1283 #define DWT_COMP_REG(base,index) ((base)->COMPARATOR[index].COMP)
1284 #define DWT_MASK_REG(base,index) ((base)->COMPARATOR[index].MASK)
1285 #define DWT_FUNCTION_REG(base,index) ((base)->COMPARATOR[index].FUNCTION)
1286  /* end of group DWT_Register_Accessor_Macros */
